29:58.379 --> 30:02.424
Specific details of how it progressed
after the dorm-room episode.

30:02.592 --> 30:04.718
Well, after the first incident. . .

30:04.886 --> 30:10.808
. ..she was sent to the university
hospital for testing and observation.

30:46.761 --> 30:50.722
Emily once told me that in her
