34:54.300 --> 34:58.220
So much of what we shared
was like a nightmare. . .

34:58.387 --> 35:01.348
. ..but l wouldn't give up
a single minute l spent with her.

35:03.518 --> 35:06.019
She woke me up, you know?

35:06.187 --> 35:10.690
To things l never felt before,
