41:15.347 --> 41:16.890
Ready to proceed?

41:18.017 --> 41:19.392
Yes, Your Honor.

41:19.560 --> 41:22.187
Dr. Briggs, please state
your qualifications for the court.

41:22.354 --> 41:24.564
l have advanced degrees
in medicine...

41:24.732 --> 41:27.650
. ..psychiatry and neurology
from Johns Hopkins. . .

41:27.818 --> 41:31.946
. ..and l have had three books
