to be sure. . .

42:28.796 --> 42:31.172
. ..but one that l have witnessed
numerous times.

42:31.340 --> 42:35.134
-Emily was epileptic and psychotic?
-Yes.

42:35.302 --> 42:38.805
Explain how this psychotic epileptic
disorder would manifest itself.

42:38.973 --> 42:41.808
