44:23.577 --> 44:25.244
-Objection. Argumentative.
-Sustained.

44:25.412 --> 44:29.374
When Emily chose
to stop her medical treatment.. .

44:29.541 --> 44:31.584
. ..what do you think
should've been done?

44:31.752 --> 44:33.503
Upon recognizing her condition...

44:33.671 --> 44:36.881
. .. l would have tranquilized her
and force-fed her.

44:37.049 --> 44:38.383
