44:38.550 --> 44:41.094
. .. l would've treated her
with electroconvulsive therapy.

44:41.261 --> 44:44.180
Electroshock treatment. You would've
done this against her will?

44:46.016 --> 44:47.392
To save her life?

44:50.437 --> 44:52.271
Absolutely.

45:01.031 --> 45:02.532
Nothing further.

45:05.494 --> 45:07.870
The witness may step down.

45:09.206 --> 45:12.959
Your Honor, l offer into evidence this
photograph as People's Exhibit 3-A.

45:13.127 --> 45:14.794
And having done so, the people rest.

45:14.962 --> 45:16.921
The photograph is entered
into evidence.

45:17.089 --> 45:22.051
We are recessed until
tomorrow morning, 9:30 sharp...

45:22.219 --> 45:25.138
. ..at which time the defense
