50:27.441 --> 50:29.608
Who did she mean by "they"?

50:30.527 --> 50:33.446
The forces that were
in control of her.

50:33.613 --> 50:35.948
That were inside her.

50:37.492 --> 50:39.035
You know, the demons.

50:41.121 --> 50:43.289
Tell us what else happened
that night.

50:47.294 --> 50:49.795
l walked her back to her dorm...

50:50.422 --> 50:53.215
. ..and she seemed really nervous
and scared.

50:53.383 --> 50:57.219
So l held her for a while,
trying to calm her down.

50:57.387 --> 51:02.892
l fell asleep, but when l woke up,
she wasn't beside me.

51:15.906 --> 51:17.490
Emily?

51:29.669 --> 51:31.212
Hey.

51:35.300 --> 51:37.259
Can you hear me?

51:49.231 --> 51:51.857
l called her father, and he told me
to bring Emily home.

51:54.444 --> 51:56.737
Jason and l put Emily to bed...

51:56.905 --> 51:59.115
...hoping she would sleep.

51:59.282 --> 52:01.283
And when did Father Moore
become involved?

52:03.078 --> 52:05.162
Emily stayed home after that.

52:05.330 --> 52:09.458
She didn't return to school,
and she kept getting worse.

52:09.626 --> 52:14.296
Eventually, when she didn't get better,
we called our priest, Father Moore.

52:15.090 --> 52:17.716
When he arrived,
l sent my daughter Alice upstairs...

52:17.884 --> 52:20.261
...to see if Emily was awake.

52:29.729 --> 52:31.063
Emily?

52:34.276 --> 52:36.235
Can l come in?

52:50.375 --> 52:53.544
-Our Father, who art in heaven--
-Emily?

52:57.883 --> 53:00.593
Father Moore is here.
Can you come downstairs?

53:00.760 --> 53:02.970
--as it is in heaven.

53:03.138 --> 53:06.557
Give us this day our daily bread. . . .

53:55.232 --> 53:56.523
Emily, can you hear me?

54:12.624 --> 54:13.999
Let's get her off the floor.

54:15.335 --> 54:16.502
Alice, no!

54:29.432 --> 54:32.518
l am the one who dwells within.

54:34.688 --> 54:38.816
And l am the one who comes
in His name.

54:40.694 --> 54:44.405
Think you can force me out, priest?

54:45.573 --> 54:46.782
Try.

54:48.994 --> 54:50.661
l dare you.

55:52.390 --> 55:55.601
You've suffered a terrible loss,
Mr. Rose. l know this is difficult.

55:55.769 --> 55:58.145
So thank you for being here today.

55:58.313 --> 55:59.855
